### How Can I Find Long-Tail Keywords for My Blog Content?

To find long-tail keywords for your blog content, type specific keywords into the Google search bar. Google will show related searches as you type, and you can scroll to the bottom for more suggestions. Compile a list of these keywords to plan your blog content.

### What Is the Ideal Length for Title Tags and Meta Descriptions?

The ideal length for title tags and meta descriptions is 60-70 characters for title tags and up to 160 characters for meta descriptions. Start the title tag with your chosen keyword and make the meta description engaging with a call to action or question.

